{"id": "1356548092450832385", "channel_id": "1356548092450832385", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "感謝各位守密人的支持！\n《忘卻前夜》OST：深港幽靈之船，今日發佈～歡迎大家收聽、下載及分享～如果有基於OST的二次創作，也歡迎分享給我們！ （二創請遵照同人規則，OST內容請勿商用）\n\n忘卻前夜OST：深港幽靈之船\n一艘遠航的行船，要將眾人帶往何方？\n那純白的神女，正坐在高高的桅杆上歌唱。\n貪婪、癡妄、掙扎與背叛，她視若無睹，她不歌唱命運的翻覆，她只歌唱，那老船長的歸航。\n\n作曲：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\n規劃：B.I.A.V. Studio\n\n——◆——◆—— ◆◆◆ ——◆——◆——\n\nThank you for your support!\n\n《Morimens》OST：《Ghost Ship of Deep Harbor》 was released today. \nWelcome everyone to listen, download and share. If you have secondary creations based on the OST, please also share them with us!\n (Please follow the rules of the fandom for secondary creations, and do not use the OST content for commercial purposes)\n\n《Morimens》OST：《Ghost Ship of Deep Harbor》 \nWhere will a ship on a long voyage take everyone?\nThe pure white goddess was sitting on the tall mast and singing.\nShe turned a blind eye to greed, delusion, struggle and betrayal. She did not sing about the ups and downs of fate, but only sang about the old captain's homecoming.\n\nComposer：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\nPlanning：B.I.A.V. Studio", "timestamp": "2025-04-01T08:37:48.685000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 12}, {"emoji": "💛", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}], "attachments": [{"id": "1356548093373583390", "filename": "OST-.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 5001828, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1356548092450832385/1356548093373583390/OST-.png?ex=69ccd95c&is=69cb87dc&hm=1bd63bff12f6849cfcf8d8ece9f99d4411eed5edb4746d469d166f2d5f859445&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1356548092450832385", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：深港幽靈之船", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1356548533385297982", "channel_id": "1356548092450832385", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**02.淵海淑女-Lady of the Abyssal-**\n\n身為淑女，當然要時時刻刻保持優雅！\n當然，我的意思是，淑女做什麼，什麼就是優雅！\nAs a lady, of course you must always be elegant!\nOf course, what I mean is that whatever a lady does is elegant!", "timestamp": "2025-04-01T08:39:33.812000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1356548533020397578", "filename": "2.-Lady_of_the_Abyssal-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 25656402, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1356548092450832385/1356548533020397578/2.-Lady_of_the_Abyssal-.wav?ex=69ccd9c5&is=69cb8845&hm=4c98a65b5e958d2d8587115f1c6861e02c5486b09777f1f211f2f6aea7dc1aea&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1356548092450832385", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：深港幽靈之船", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1356548645029281923", "channel_id": "1356548092450832385", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**03.詭光帷幕-Veil of Eerie Light-**\n\n耐心，謹慎，切莫讓五彩斑斕的光迷了眼。\nBe patient, be cautious, and don't let the colorful light dazzle your eyes.", "timestamp": "2025-04-01T08:40:00.430000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1356548644526100550", "filename": "3.-Veil_of_Eerie_Light-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 18382180, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1356548092450832385/1356548644526100550/3.-Veil_of_Eerie_Light-.wav?ex=69ccd9e0&is=69cb8860&hm=5934b1d3cd8a4ef87f7c30c481bb20230b3a7e96ca0e76742083af7164d7d91b&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1356548092450832385", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：深港幽靈之船", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1356548777686863944", "channel_id": "1356548092450832385", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**04.幻海潮湧-Ethereal Sea Tides-**\n\n幻光的潮在天體的牽引下編織成帷幕，蹈海的詭物踏浪而來。\nThe tide of phantom light weaves into a curtain under the traction of the celestial body, and the sea-walking monsters come on the waves.", "timestamp": "2025-04-01T08:40:32.058000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1356548777208709220", "filename": "4.-Ethereal_Sea_Tides-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 36862224, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1356548092450832385/1356548777208709220/4.-Ethereal_Sea_Tides-.wav?ex=69ccd9ff&is=69cb887f&hm=e6651d029f14aa2f3b14ecb9e5d4c150d91648f8e0c496f20aa027696a220f42&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1356548092450832385", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：深港幽靈之船", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1356548844531351624", "channel_id": "1356548092450832385", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**05.億萬禱言-A Million Prayers-**\n\n王啊，我已遵循預言等待了萬年，可未來為何依舊遙不可及？\n我本應繼續祈禱，但請原諒我，我已經等不及了。\nKing, I have followed the prophecy and waited for ten thousand years, but why is the future still out of reach?\nI should have continued to pray, but please forgive me, I can't wait any longer.", "timestamp": "2025-04-01T08:40:47.995000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1356548843910725773", "filename": "5.-A_Million_Prayers-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 25868580, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1356548092450832385/1356548843910725773/5.-A_Million_Prayers-.wav?ex=69ccda0f&is=69cb888f&hm=9ea32336d3c9cbc345494900ef23fd7614a11ba2ec63e91432721c18fe039973&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1356548092450832385", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：深港幽靈之船", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1356549047262904440", "channel_id": "1356548092450832385", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**06.眠於深淵之王-King in the Abyss-**\n\n王至高無上，王威權無邊，王遙坐於輝煌之上，孤獨的俯視他的國。\nThe king is supreme, the king has boundless power, the king sits on the glory, and looks down on his kingdom alone.", "timestamp": "2025-04-01T08:41:36.330000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1356549046671769692", "filename": "6.-King_in_the_Abyss-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 38249868, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1356548092450832385/1356549046671769692/6.-King_in_the_Abyss-.wav?ex=69ccda40&is=69cb88c0&hm=909ddb0fbc442c6b455cbae8d3e7869f49eea55f01a34e5ed11549e99f59a356&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1356548092450832385", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：深港幽靈之船", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1356549216293621781", "channel_id": "1356548092450832385", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**07.尊榮神母-Divine Mother-**\n\n上天已賜下尊貴的神母，用以接我們到祂的國。\n讚美「吾主」！\nGod has given us the noble Mother of God to take us to His kingdom.\nPraise \"My Lord\"!", "timestamp": "2025-04-01T08:42:16.630000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "pray", "emoji_id": "1356053116260454534", "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1356549215932780586", "filename": "7.-Divine_Mother-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 47860218, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1356548092450832385/1356549215932780586/7.-Divine_Mother-.wav?ex=69ccda68&is=69cb88e8&hm=59077c11aa7dc484918ca8772702334a9c58c6dd908e8e0d2be9877dccc3f094&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1356548092450832385", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：深港幽靈之船", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1356549270047690763", "channel_id": "1356548092450832385", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**08.覆海決意-Prophecy Defiance-**\n\n淵海的淑女決心貫徹自己的意志，赴向遙不可及的自由。\nThe Lady of the Deep Sea is determined to carry out her will and go to the unreachable freedom.", "timestamp": "2025-04-01T08:42:29.446000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1356549269766541364", "filename": "8.-Prophecy_Defiance-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 7307564, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1356548092450832385/1356549269766541364/8.-Prophecy_Defiance-.mp3?ex=69ccda75&is=69cb88f5&hm=f70eaa070e141c677bef0611b437b6b0b98af0e94291936a263ce5547adfda41&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1356548092450832385", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：深港幽靈之船", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1356549386003550309", "channel_id": "1356548092450832385", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**09.瀆神誓言-Blasphemous Oath-**\n\n卑賤的小偷盜取了王的力量，妄圖阻礙偉大的儀式。\n不敬之贗品，當以死謝罪！\nThe lowly thief stole the power of the king and tried to hinder the great ceremony.\nThe disrespectful counterfeit should die to pay for his crime!", "timestamp": "2025-04-01T08:42:57.092000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1356549385743499315", "filename": "9.-Blasphemous_Oath-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 19820424, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1356548092450832385/1356549385743499315/9.-Blasphemous_Oath-.wav?ex=69ccda91&is=69cb8911&hm=ff60efcaac14facb54c7286e942699e2043c6da57e2b138c755ba521f2d79a5e&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1356548092450832385", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：深港幽靈之船", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1356549460225687614", "channel_id": "1356548092450832385", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**10.永恆王土-The Eternal Kingdom-**\n\n美麗！富饒！理想之鄉利莫里亞！\n強大！堅韌！神王庇護利莫里亞！\n偉哉！偉哉！永恆之國利莫里亞！\nBeautiful! Rich! The ideal land of Lemuria!\nPowerful! Tough! The God King protects Lemuria!\nGreat! Great! The eternal country of Lemuria!", "timestamp": "2025-04-01T08:43:14.788000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1356549459785289778", "filename": "10.-The_Eternal_Kingdom-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 9565484, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1356548092450832385/1356549459785289778/10.-The_Eternal_Kingdom-.mp3?ex=69ccdaa2&is=69cb8922&hm=96a49ebc868c96ce6d2d3a1c96f587f45f22e137bd48d56bffeba2617ba4429a&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1356548092450832385", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：深港幽靈之船", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1356549572092100640", "channel_id": "1356548092450832385", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**11.執妄審判-The Judge of Delusions-**\n\n你曾向我許諾過，你們向我許諾過。\n如果我不能拯救利莫里亞，那就一起，為它陪葬吧！\nYou promised me, you promised me.\nIf I can't save Lemuria, then we will be buried together for it!", "timestamp": "2025-04-01T08:43:41.459000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1356549572045832252", "filename": "11.-The_Judge_of_Delusions-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 17018886, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1356548092450832385/1356549572045832252/11.-The_Judge_of_Delusions-.wav?ex=69ccdabd&is=69cb893d&hm=0e76a3674dc2fff3f9acc3eeb9c01578db681e5e75cdd65f5f02544dae3b301e&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1356548092450832385", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘卻前夜OST：深港幽靈之船", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
